    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab> In nomine domini Dei et salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/118">Hludovvicus</persName> et
                            <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/9">Hlutario</persName> divina
                        ordinantes providentja <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperatores</rs> augustos,
                        anno imperii eorum Deo propitio vigisimo et quartodecimo, septimo kalendas
                        augustas, indictione undecima .â€¦ Et ideo ego <persName
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Priests"><name ref="Albertus"
                            >Alibertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiter</rs> filius quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes de Bardi">Iohanni</name></persName> de <placeName
                            key="#Casalia #Houses #Curtes #Fruits/vegetables #Cereals #Wine #Forests #Landed_possessions #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Hay/fodder"
                            ref="#places/1900">Bardi</placeName>, nullum me conpellente nec vim
                        inferente sed propria mea deliberatjonis arbitrio, sola me considerante Dei
                        omnipotentis misericordia et remedio anime meae vel parentorum meorum, volo
                        ut omnibus rebus meis quem habere visus sum in suprascripto loco Bardi seu
                        in <placeName
                            key="#Casalia #Churches #Curtes #Fruits/vegetables #Cereals #Wine #Forests #Landed_possessions #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Hay/fodder"
                            ref="#places/1542">Odolo</placeName> vel per aliis singulis <rs
                            key="#Casalia">casalibus</rs> nec non et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1110">beatorum martirum
                            Protasii et Gervasii</orgName> situm in ipso loco Odolo deveniat in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/47">beatissimorum omnium
                            apostolorum et Christi confessores Silvestri</orgName> situs <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15">Nonantula</placeName>
                        <rs key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/38">Motinense</placeName>, ubi
                        nunc tempore vir venerabilis <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries"
                            ref="#people/199">Ansfrit</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> esse videtur, a presenti die deveniat in
                        alimonia pauperum vel in stipentja monachorum ibidem Deum deservientibus.
                        Idest tam <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>, habitationis mee in Bardi vel alias
                        tectoras seu per aliis singulis casalibus, una cum suprascripta ecclesia
                        Sanctorum Protasii et Gervasii, <rs key="#Curtes">curtis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortas</rs>, areis, clausuras, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, pascuis,
                            <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, montibus et
                        vallibus seu adiciis, ripis, ropinis ac padulibus, cultum et incoltum,
                        divisum et indivisum <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >usibusque aquarum</rs> vel puteos, cum finibus vel terminibus, una cum
                        singulas <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casas massaricias</rs> vel <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sortibus</rs> tam in Odolo vel in Bardi vel
                        per aliis singulis casalibus, <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/1902"><geogName key="#Fines">Castro
                                Arquensis</geogName></placeName> vel finibus <placeName key="#Fines"
                            ref="#places/43"><geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/1500"
                                >Placentina</geogName></placeName> vel in finibus <placeName
                            key="#Fines" ref="#places/191"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/1503">Regiensis</geogName></placeName>, loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/1543" key="#Casalia">Arceto</placeName>,
                        anteposito in <placeName key="#Casalia" ref="#places/1598"
                            >Trimiolo</placeName> et in <placeName key="#Casalia" ref="#places/1599"
                            >Varianise</placeName> ..10.., nam aliis omnibus rebus iuris meis tam de
                        paterna vel materna substantia, sive per conparationem, donatjonem,
                        comutatjonem vel per qualecumque ingenio seu tinore ad me devolutes sunt et
                        me de inter germanis meis vel nepotibus in divisione obvenire dinuscitur,
                        seu arboribus olivarum una cum omni iure, adiacentiis et pertinentiis suis,
                        cum accessionibus vel egressoras suarum, omnia et ex omnibus ut supra dixi
                        in integrum deveniat in iam dicto sancto et venerabile monasterio pro anima
                        mea vel parentorum meorum a presenti die, anteposito in suprascriptas locas
                        Trimiolo et in Varianise ut supra mihi reservavi, nam aliis omnibus rebus
                        meis superius conprehensis, ubicumque inventum vel proqueritum fuerit, omnia
                        et ex omnibus in integrum habeat ipso superdicto monasterio ab hac die in
                        perpetuum teneat, possideat, vindicet atque defendat. Et pro maiore
                        firmitatem, iurata voce, dico per omnipotentem Deum et inseperabile sanctam
                        Trinitatem Sedemque sanctam apostolica et sanctas quattuor Evvangelias,
                        numquam sum venturus causandi aut removendi, iudicandi, sed omni in tempore
                        firmis et stabilis permaneat. Et non liceat nolle quod semel volui sed quod
                        semel ad me factum vel conscriptum est inviolabiliter modis omnibus
                        conservare promitto. Quam vero cartola donationis seu offersionis meae,
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scrivere</rs> rogavi in qua subter propria manu mea
                        scripsi et una cum <rs key="#Witness">testibusque</rs> ad me rogitis obtuli
                        roborandum. Actum ad curte ipsius monasterii qui dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/1540" key="#Curtes"><geogName ref="#estates/1114"
                                key="#Curtes">Ponte Marmoriolo</geogName></placeName>, die et
                        indictione suprascripta undecima, feliciter. + Ego Alibertus presbiter in
                        hanc cartolam donationis atque ofertjonis a me facta relegi et manu propria
                        subscripsi. Signum + manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gausbertus"
                                >Gausperti</name></persName> germano ispius Aliberti presbitero
                        rogatus testis. Signum + manus <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Garipertus">Gariperti</name></persName> de <placeName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#places/1547">Aucis</placeName> rogatus testis.
                        Signum + manus <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Audoaldus"
                                >Audoaldi</name></persName> de <placeName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#places/1545">Vereniano</placeName> rogatus testis finibus
                            <placeName key="#Witness #Fines" ref="#places/9"><geogName
                                key="#Witness #Fines" ref="#estates/1449"
                            >Brexiana</geogName></placeName>. Signum + manus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodemarius">Rodemari</name></persName> de
                            <placeName key="#Witness" ref="#places/1548">Dungiano</placeName>
                        finibus Brexiana testis. + Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Rodiperto">Rodeberto</name></persName> presbiter rogatus ad
                        Aliberto presbiter germano meo subscripsi. + Ego qui supra Iohannes notarius
                        scripsi post roborata et tradita conplevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
